summary:
I am an Enthusiastic, Optimistic, Dedicated, and Versatile Young soon-graduating Korean student with Diverse and Outstanding background, and Cooperate attitude to team work. 
With 3 years of full experience for living in Abu Dhabi, I definitely have a great understanding of mindset of residents, history, and current market situations. I wish to find a job where I can apply and use my personal skills to meet the expectation of the job position. I wish to find a job in semi-government companies in Abu Dhabi.
